дзора по Белгородской области, БелМВЛ, руководители и сотрудники пищевых предприятий Белгородской, Курской областей, профессора Саратовского Государственного Аграрного Университета, а также преподаватели, студенты и аспиранты Белгородской Сельскохозяйственной Академии. Был проведен мастер-класс по методам применения дезинфицирующих и моющих средств для санитарной обработки пищевых и других объектов ветнадзора. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>По окончании семинара участникам были вручены образцы средств и сертификаты о прохождении обучения.</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title=\"начало семинара\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0220%20-%20копия.jpg\" alt=\"начало семинара\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title=\"вводная инструкция перед дезинфекцией\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0240.jpg\" alt=\"вводная инструкция перед дезинфекцией\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<h4><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-weight: normal;\"> </span></h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-weight: normal;\"><img title=\"начало регистрации\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0286.jpg\" alt=\"начало регистрации\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>','','','1312'),(4878,4,'«Санитарно-гигиеническая безопасность на объектах ветнадзора и пищевых предприятиях»','<h4><strong>Уважаемые друзья, коллеги, партнеры!</strong></h4>\r\n<p><strong>С 25 по 26 июня в г. Белгород на базе факультета ветеринарной медицины Белгородской Государственной Сельскохозяйственной Академии им.В.Я.Горина состоялся семинар на тему «Санитарно-гигиеническая безопасность на объектах ветнадзора и пищевых предприятиях» организованный компанией «СпецСинтез», совместно с  факультетом ветеринарной медицины, информационно-консультационным центром Белгородской Сельскохозяйственной Академии. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>Участниками семинара стали представители Управления ветеринарии, Управления Россельхознадзора по Белгородской области, БелМВЛ, руководители и сотрудники пищевых предприятий Белгородской, Курской областей, профессора Саратовского Государственного Аграрного Университета, а также преподаватели, студенты и аспиранты Белгородской Сельскохозяйственной Академии. Был проведен мастер-класс по методам применения дезинфицирующих и моющих средств для санитарной обработки пищевых и других объектов ветнадзора. </strong></p>\r\n<p><strong>По окончании семинара участникам были вручены образцы средств и сертификаты о прохождении обучения.</strong></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title=\"начало семинара\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0220%20-%20копия.jpg\" alt=\"начало семинара\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p><img title=\"вводная инструкция перед дезинфекцией\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0240.jpg\" alt=\"вводная инструкция перед дезинфекцией\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></p>\r\n<h4><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-weight: normal;\"> </span></h4>\r\n<p><span style=\"line-height: 1.5em; font-weight: normal;\"><img title=\"начало регистрации\" src=\"assets/template/images/IMG_0286.jpg\" alt=\"начало регистрации\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\" /></span></p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>','','','1312'),(4879,1,'International specialized exhibition of the medical equipment, tools and medicinal preparations of MEDICA 2013','<p>From November 20 to November 22, 2013 in the city of Düsseldorf (Germany) took place the largest world exhibition in the medicine sphere – MEDICA – 2013<br />This year the exhibition was visited by 132000 people, took part 4641 exhibitors representing 66 countries. In the territory of 17 pavilions the full range of new products for qualitative and operational medical care in hospitals and out-patient establishments was presented.</p>\r\n<p><br />Within held events, conference of \"Physician\" took place. As Joachim Schäfer, the managing director of Messe Düsseldorf told at a press conference: \"Conference of the PHYSICIAN which regularly attracts some thousands of participants, was still well-known in Germany. Now more than a half of visitors to MEDICA arrive from abroad. Organizers I note body height of number of visitors from Russia\" Subjects of conference included problems of management of sisterly leaving, the problems bound to aging of the population and some other.</p>\r\n<p><br />At the company stand Olimpus, Carle Chtorts took place brisk discussion about current trends of operation and processing of endoscopic equipment. Specialists of the Spetssintez company and representatives of the manufacturing company of endoscopic equipment agreed in opinion that processing of difficult and expensive technique demands the trained staff, superfine reagents, the reliable washing equipment.</p>\r\n<p><br />As a result of visit of the international forum by specialists of the Spetssintez company new perspective offers for the Russian treatment-and-prophylactic establishments were prepared.</p>','','','1122'),(4879,4,'International specialized exhibition of the medical equipment, tools and medicinal preparations of MEDICA 2013','<p>From November 20 to November 22, 2013 in the city of Düsseldorf (Germany) took place the largest world exhibition in the medicine sphere – MEDICA – 2013<br />This year the exhibition was visited by 132000 people, took part 4641 exhibitors representing 66 countries. In the territory of 17 pavilions the full range of new products for qualitative and operational medical care in hospitals and out-patient establishments was presented.</p>\r\n<p><br />Within held events, conference of \"Physician\" took place. As Joachim Schäfer, the managing director of Messe Düsseldorf told at a press conference: \"Conference of the PHYSICIAN which regularly attracts some thousands of participants, was still well-known in Germany. Now more than a half of visitors to MEDICA arrive from abroad. Organizers I note body height of number of visitors from Russia\" Subjects of conference included problems of management of sisterly leaving, the problems bound to aging of the population and some other.</p>\r\n<p><br />At the company stand Olimpus, Carle Chtorts took place brisk discussion about current trends of operation and processing of endoscopic equipment. Specialists of the Spetssintez company and representatives of the manufacturing company of endoscopic equipment agreed in opinion that processing of difficult and expensive technique demands the trained staff, superfine reagents, the reliable washing equipment.</p>\r\n<p><br />As a result of visit of the international forum by specialists of the Spetssintez company new perspective offers for the Russian treatment-and-prophylactic establishments were prepared.</p>','','','1122'),(4880,1,'Health care-2013 exhibition','<p>Dear friends, colleagues, partners!</p>\r\n<p>We invite you to visit our stand at the 23rd international Health care-2013 exhibition which will take place from December 09 to December 13, 2013 in the Central exhibition complex \"Expotsentr\" Moscow.</p>\r\n<p>We wait for you at our stand 1G40 in Pavilion No. 1.</p>\r\n<p>You can study more detailed information on an exhibition here - <a href=\"http://www.zdravo-expo.ru/\">http://www.zdravo-expo.ru/</a></p>','','','1123'),(4880,4,'Health care-2013 exhibition','<p>Dear friends, colleagues, partners!</p>\r\n<p>We invite you to visit our stand at the 23rd international Health care-2013 exhibition which will take place from December 09 to December 13, 2013 in the Central exhibition complex \"Expotsentr\" Moscow.</p>\r\n<p>We wait for you at our stand 1G40 in Pavilion No. 1.</p>\r\n<p>You can study more detailed information on an exhibition here - <a href=\"http://www.zdravo-expo.ru/\">http://www.zdravo-expo.ru/</a></p>','','','1123'),(4881,1,'Participation in the Health care-2013 exhibition','<p>From December 9 to December 13, 2013 in the Central exhibition 